<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Vulcan" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Vulcan,</orth> the god who presided over the art of forging: <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.187" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 187</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 168</bibl> (<emph>V. and his wife,</emph> i. e. Venus). <bibl n="shak. tro 5.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 170</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 89</bibl> (<emph>--'s badge,</emph> i. e. the horns of cuckoldom). <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 89</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>